title: Sally Wing Russ Martin
description:
THE OBSESSION OF SALLY WING
RUSS MARTIN
Copyright 1983

She must take the lives of other human beings. The Organization thinks it controls her horrible need, but the Organization is wrong.

Only one woman knows the truth.

That woman is sworn to the destruction of the Organization. Will she succeed before the demonic power has achieved its world domain? Can she possibly destroy the age-old evil that has created

THE OBSESSION OF SALLY WING
